5201-b377-4850-8aba-886bdb4a5621.jpg?v=1710421057" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_0faf5201-b377-4850-8aba-886bdb4a5621.jpg?v=1710421057 1536w" width="1750" height="1167" alt="Master UK Standards with eLearning Compliance Training - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Master UK Standards with eLearning Compliance Training - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-146_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-147_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by valeriygoncharukphoto via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-149_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Virtual training is defined by its use of digital platforms to deliver educational content, enabling remote access to knowledge and skills. This approach leverages technology to offer dynamic, interactive learning experiences tailored to meet the individual needs of learners.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-151_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-152_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-153_ pf-heading-1-h3">The statistical landscape</h3><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-155_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-156_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_99763f4b-d549-4b54-abe8-c5d8ba62840a.jpg?v=1710421075" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_99763f4b-d549-4b54-abe8-c5d8ba62840a.jpg?v=1710421075 1536w" width="1875" height="1250" alt="Discover the Future: Virtual Learning Platforms UK for Innovative Education - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Discover the Future: Virtual Learning Platforms UK for Innovative Education - The Mandatory Training Group UK